{"id":278734,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/【图说天朝】初一突然有信仰/","date":"2013-02-11T03:53:30Z","modified":"2013-02-11T03:53:31Z","title":"【图说天朝】初一突然有“信仰”","content":"<p>2月10日大年初一，北京雍和宫约有7、8万人抢烧新年的头柱香。雍和宫是北京最大的藏传佛教寺院，也是香火最旺的地方之一。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e5%88%9d%e4%b8%80%e7%aa%81%e7%84%b6%e6%9c%89%e4%bf%a1%e4%bb%b0/39536_231463_781243/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-278735\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-278735\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/39536_231463_781243.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/39536_231463_781243.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/39536_231463_781243-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/39536_231463_781243-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/39536_231463_781243-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 950px) 100vw, 950px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">2月10日，广州光孝寺，民众抢烧“第一柱香”过后垃圾遍地。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e5%88%9d%e4%b8%80%e7%aa%81%e7%84%b6%e6%9c%89%e4%bf%a1%e4%bb%b0/8ne0u2jg00an0001/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-278736\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-278736\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8NE0U2JG00AN0001-1024x669.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8NE0U2JG00AN0001-1024x669.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8NE0U2JG00AN0001-300x196.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8NE0U2JG00AN0001-230x150.jpg 230w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/8NE0U2JG00AN0001.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,